Package com.schibsted.android.sdk.exceptions

Exception Summary
SPiDApiException Signals that a API exception has occurred in SPiD
SPiDAuthorizationAlreadyRunningException Signals that a authorization request is already running
SPiDDeviceFingerprintException Signals that there was a error trying to generate a device fingerprint
SPiDException Base class for all exceptions in SPiD.
SPiDInvalidRequestException Signals that there was a problem with the request to SPiD
SPiDInvalidResponseException Signals that there was a problem with the response received from SPiD
SPiDKeychainException Signals that there was a problem encrypting/decrypting the access token from SharedPreferences
SPiDOAuthException Signals that there was a problem with OAuth 2.0, see http://tools.ietf.org/html/draft-ietf-oauth-v2
SPiDUserAbortedLoginException Signals that the user aborted login
